snippet.title: Murtaza Ali Shah
snippet.description:
Murtaza Ali Shah is one of the leading reporters in Pakistani media. He is known for his exclusive reporting on Pakistani political, social and cultural affairs from London. This is an official page.

You can follow him on:
https://www.youtube.com/MurtazaAliShah
Twitter link: https://twitter.com/MurtazaViews
Facebook Link: https://facebook.com/MurtazaViews/
Instagram Link: https://www.instagram.com/murtazaalishah1/
The News: https://www.thenews.com.pk/writer/murtaza-ali-shah
Geo News: https://www.geo.tv/writer/murtaza-ali-shah

Stories & tips? ams0409@gmail.com
